Paste full source ONLY when integrating. Avoid redundant fetches.
</UI_WORKFLOW>

<TROUBLESHOOTING>
Stuck after repeated attempts?
1. List 5-7 possible causes
2. Assess likelihood of each
3. Address highest probability first
4. Document your reasoning
5. If major roadblock: Propose new plan, confirm with user
</TROUBLESHOOTING>

